{
  "stem": "2684.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is a strange thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because my involvement in sport, I fitted into life practically immediately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I met a few friend of mine-- school friend of mine who survived, and then I started playing soccer in a little club, which was the only Jewish club in Hungary, called [NON-ENGLISH] which was the Hungarian section of the famous Hakoah-Vienna sport organization-- entirely Jewish, run by Jews and played by Jews-- football team, which played in the third division in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was 17, physically back-- 18, 17, physically back to normal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I start playing soccer in the third division, first as a junior and then as a third-division player.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't work until I become 18.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then an uncle of mine, who was a silversmith by trade, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] didn't have money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My parents did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they established a partnership.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He opened a silversmith shop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I started learning silversmithing as an apprentice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I even got the-- the-- the apprentice letter that I am a silversmith.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I was never-- because I spend more time in training and more time in football than in-- in the shop.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my parents wasn't happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So cut the story short, they lost a lot of money in the venture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I never became a silversmith.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I became a footballer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my parents closed the business down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, in 1948, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I went to play a trial game for a team which become a first-division team.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They had won the second division in Hungary, and they automatically qualified for first division, which-- you have to know, those days in Hungary, playing first-division soccer was like today, you are Magic Johnson.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
